"Goya might be the biggest fish in the pond, but it is not the only fish in the pond... we are all free to do with our frijoles as we wish." https://t.co/8GmqVCtiUw https://t.co/KrKAALIS5I

text:
More research emerged this week in potential support of using the tuberculosis vaccine Bacillus Calmette-Guerin as a tool against Covid-19.

Researchers found that countries with many people who've gotten the vaccine have had less mortality from Covid-19. https://t.co/h7HmXuLCgB
